{"arkId":"cl010095611","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010095611","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Vestale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Vestale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1787","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [SCULPT] Galerie des Grands Hommes (ex-salle 29)","room":"Galerie des Grands Hommes (ex-salle 29), Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 0","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1787,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Houdon, Jean Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1741","place":"Versailles","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1828","place":"Paris ","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q318741"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 4718","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statue","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Sur la plinthe, \u00e0 gauche : \u00ab houdon f. 1787 \u00bb","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":"","shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Ex\u00e9cut\u00e9e en 1787 et expos\u00e9e au Salon de cette ann\u00e9e (n\u00b0257) : \u00ab une Vestale \u00bb ; premi\u00e8re vente de l\u2019atelier de Houdon, 8 octobre 1795, n\u00b072  ; vente anonyme, Paris, 13 f\u00e9vrier 1834, n\u00b082 ; vente du marchand Latapi\u00e9, Paris, 7-9 d\u00e9cembre 1854, n\u00b0149.  La Vestale est signal\u00e9e \u00ab en vente chez X rue de Clichy en avril 1901 \u00bb ; acquise par les fr\u00e8res Duveen et vraisemblablement emport\u00e9e \u00e0 Londres dans leur galerie ; vendue le 24 juin 1901 au banquier collectionneur John Pierpont Morgan (1837-1913), qui installa l\u2019oeuvre \u00e0 New York ; \u00e0 sa mort en 1913, transmise \u00e0 son fils John Pierpont Morgan Jr. (1867-1943); mise en d\u00e9p\u00f4t en 1925 au Metropolitan Museum of Art ; acquise par Georges Wildenstein (en tout cas apr\u00e8s 1936, et vraisemblablement apr\u00e8s la mort de son dernier propri\u00e9taire en 1943). D\u00e9clar\u00e9e \u0022tr\u00e9sor national\u0022 le 31 mars 2004. Acquise \u00e0 New York en mars 2005 par le groupe Axa pour le mus\u00e9e du Louvre.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Wildenstein, Georges","note":"","role":", Antiquaire \/ Marchand d\u0027art"},{"value":"M. Pierpont-Morgan, John Sr","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"22\/10\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"09\/12\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"material":[{"value":"marbre"}],"objectType":[{"value":"statue"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Torres, Pascal ; Mathieux, N\u00e9guine ; Pomar\u00e8de, Vincent (dir.), L\u0027Invention du Louvre, cat. exp. (Hong Kong (Chine), Heritage Museum, 2017), Hong Kong, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, 2017","bibliographyDate":"2017","bibliographyDetail":"p. 61, p. 62, fig. 13","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Houdon (1741-1828). Statue